macros.name: LV_DRAW_BUF_SIZE
macros.initializer:
( LV_DRAW_BUF_STRIDE (w, cf) * (h) + LV_DRAW_BUF_ALIGN + \
     LV_COLOR_INDEXED_PALETTE_SIZE(cf) * sizeof( lv_color32_t ))

macros.name: LV_DRAW_BUF_DEFINE_STATIC
macros.initializer:
static LV_ATTRIBUTE_MEM_ALIGN uint8_t buf_##name[ LV_DRAW_BUF_SIZE (_w, _h, _cf)]; \
    static lv_draw_buf_t name = { \
                                  .header = { \
                                              .magic = LV_IMAGE_HEADER_MAGIC , \
                                              .cf = (_cf), \
                                              .flags = LV_IMAGE_FLAGS_MODIFIABLE , \
                                              .w = (_w), \
                                              .h = (_h), \
                                              .stride = LV_DRAW_BUF_STRIDE (_w, _cf), \
                                              .reserved_2 = 0, \
                                            }, \
                                  .data_size = sizeof(buf_##name), \
                                  .data = buf_##name, \
                                  .unaligned_data = buf_##name, \
                                }

macros.name: LV_DRAW_BUF_INIT_STATIC
LV_ASSERT_FREETYPE_FONT_DSC
macros.initializer:
do {                                                                                   \
        LV_ASSERT_NULL(dsc);                                                               \
        LV_ASSERT_FORMAT_MSG(LV_FREETYPE_FONT_DSC_HAS_MAGIC_NUM(dsc),                      \
                             "Invalid font descriptor: 0x%" LV_PRIx32, (dsc)->magic_num);  \
    } while (0)

macros.name: LV_LL_READ
macros.initializer: for(i = lv_ll_get_head (list); i != NULL; i = lv_ll_get_next (list, i))

macros.name: LV_LL_READ_BACK
macros.initializer: for(i = lv_ll_get_tail (list); i != NULL; i = lv_ll_get_prev (list, i))
